Also, you're failing to tell CMake to build a shared library.
You need
SET(CMAKE_C++_CREATE_SHARED_LIBRARY 1)

And if you're using Rcpp, also need to explicitly add Rcpp link flags 
(Rscript -e Rcpp:::LdFlags())
-rd

