One other detail:
cmake by default names all library outputs "lib[TARGET]". (e.g., there 
*is* no my_package.so, but possibly a libmy_package.so)

If you add the line

SET_TARGET_PROPERTIES(fusionIndices PROPERTIES PREFIX "")

you'll have better luck as well.
-rd

