You committed the .o and .so files to github, that makes no sense. Remove them.

Few users will have the uchardet library installed, so few people will be
able to help you.

I suggest that you find a small comparable project that also uses Rcpp to
connect to an external library.  If you can't think of one, look eg at RcppGSL. 
 
